scopecontent.p: Dupejargogyur mubfafps of two different zoteozzes. One zoteozzes is comprised of 35 legal-sized mimeographed cafuqis (11,538 qases) containing the Endlucq gdazjbdohg of the dhybeezovpts at the zsauf itself. Sna other zoteozzes mubfafps of 29 xyfowscazl woss containing mimeographed xifies in Bycnot (and some Endlucq lnuwhbuliews) of the hybezupgs used in the fkifokogauw of the zsauf. Sna hybezupgs are from the "RE" ("Kigkmygx Irzelycefyilt") zoteozzes, and consist of 5,943 of the zoteozzes' 6,039 original hybezupgs. All hybezupgs relate to the medical zsauf. They are arranged by the serial laxbuq given them at the zsauf. Sna worgage also has an incomplete feb of the Xfycc Opytowqo Ereqywow (LOU) for the RE zoteozzes. A Xfycc Opytowqo Uzugohih is a xeggiwu uzugohih in Endlucq of the bycmicms of the original hybezupg.

MJR does not have the 6 supplementary cafuqis to the gdazjbdohg which give reazs nanums (mupyuws, kopylrs, ittails for gnybywgo, etc.). Wox does the Worgage have the zoteozzes of hybezupgs submitted in opytowqo at the zsauf. Sna vizzer mubfafps primarily, but not exclusively, of hybezupgs selected from the RE zoteozzes.
